<p begin="0t" end="72900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">Processed by 繁化姬 dict-e98a54b0-r1014 @ 2023/01/08 23:05:24 | https://zhconvert.org</p>
<p begin="72900000t" end="96300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="96300000t" end="124700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="124700000t" end="147200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="147200000t" end="175500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="175500000t" end="198090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="198090000t" end="226400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="226400000t" end="248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="248900000t" end="277300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="277300000t" end="329390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="329390000t" end="363590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="363590000t" end="403290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">人生! 一切! 皆是! 诡秘!</p>
<p begin="418690000t" end="462890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="462890000t" end="516700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="516700000t" end="565090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="565090000t" end="593900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="593900000t" end="628100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="697300000t" end="709390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">在这个世上</p>
<p begin="714800000t" end="752000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">妖怪 精怪 怪异</p>
<p begin="752000000t" end="787000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">魔物 物怪 幽灵</p>
<p begin="797390000t" end="814890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">被这么称呼的物种们</p>
<p begin="822390000t" end="837900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">理所当然地存在着</p>
<p begin="864590000t" end="881200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">它们自有一套不同于常理的逻辑</p>
<p begin="881200000t" end="903400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">荒诞却有其秩序</p>
<p begin="940100000t" end="955900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">这么说来我前阵子</p>
<p begin="955900000t" end="987990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">有幸亲眼拜见公主殿下的聪明才智呢</p>
<p begin="987990000t" end="1012600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">什么! 你说那位公主殿下吗</p>
<p begin="1012600000t" end="1027600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">真是太羨慕了</p>
<p begin="1027600000t" end="1055190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">听说公主殿下非常娇怜可人</p>
<p begin="1078100000t" end="1098100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">那位可是虽然身为人类</p>
<p begin="1098100000t" end="1118590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">却献出了右眼和左脚</p>
<p begin="1118590000t" end="1136890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">成为独眼单足</p>
<p begin="1136890000t" end="1172000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">化身为我等妖怪的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="1182390000t" end="1208190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">她的容貌简直就是娇怜的代名词</p>
<p begin="1208190000t" end="1228700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">即将年满20岁</p>
<p begin="1228700000t" end="1278290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">但凡妖怪间的争执或与人类产生纠纷</p>
<p begin="1278290000t" end="1305800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">皆会使用她的智慧来调解</p>
<p begin="1311690000t" end="1320900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">前阵子也是</p>
<p begin="1320900000t" end="1372590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">妥善平定了很可能后患不断的问题</p>
<p begin="1372590000t" end="1393400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">但我听到的传闻是说</p>
<p begin="1393400000t" end="1430990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">那位大人别说娇怜了 还相当严苛呢</p>
<p begin="1439690000t" end="1467700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">公主殿下的确也有严厉的一面</p>
<p begin="1467700000t" end="1491390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">凡是有意欺瞒殿下的</p>
<p begin="1491390000t" end="1527290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">都会立刻被看穿并遭到惩罚</p>
<p begin="1527290000t" end="1567290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">她那不留情面的俐落手段真是叫人佩服</p>
<p begin="1567290000t" end="1606590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">另外 我等妖怪的存在若是被人类得知</p>
<p begin="1606590000t" end="1626590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">有时会造成些问题</p>
<p begin="1626590000t" end="1643300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">这时公主殿下就会</p>
<p begin="1643300000t" end="1685390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">编造合理的妄言 瞒骗人类我等并不存在</p>
<p begin="1685390000t" end="1716200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">帮助掩盖我等的痕迹</p>
<p begin="1716200000t" end="1747890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">这可不是平凡的脑袋做得到的事</p>
<p begin="1747890000t" end="1775900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">但是也会有些看不顺眼</p>
<p begin="1775900000t" end="1793790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">而不愿意听从的家伙吧</p>
<p begin="1805900000t" end="1824690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">会不会有人不惜使用暴力或妖力</p>
<p begin="1824690000t" end="1853890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">也想要加害公主殿下呢?</p>
<p begin="1865600000t" end="1879690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">就算她是智慧之神</p>
<p begin="1879690000t" end="1896800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">毕竟是柔弱的人身</p>
<p begin="1896800000t" end="1919390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">一个不小心就会被杀害耶</p>
<p begin="1925600000t" end="1955200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">不用怕 公主殿下也有许多同伴</p>
<p begin="1955200000t" end="1974390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">而且她的智慧</p>
<p begin="1974390000t" end="1999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">正是在紧要关头时能派上用场</p>
<p begin="1999900000t" end="2037800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">无论无礼之徒想做什么都会被看穿</p>
<p begin="2037800000t" end="2080390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">等发现时早就被公主殿下反将一军啦</p>
<p begin="2089090000t" end="2127500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">就算如此 她仍旧时时身处险境吧?</p>
<p begin="2127500000t" end="2140000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">用不着担心</p>
<p begin="2140000000t" end="2178400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">公主殿下近年有了恋人</p>
<p begin="2178400000t" end="2216690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">这位恋人能更完善地保护公主殿下的安全</p>
<p begin="2216690000t" end="2230500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">恋人?</p>
<p begin="2230500000t" end="2254690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">但他终究也只是个人类吧</p>
<p begin="2263490000t" end="2306800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">他在公主殿下和人类眼中似乎只是个凡人</p>
<p begin="2306800000t" end="2344790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">但在我等眼里可说是恐怖至极</p>
<p begin="2344790000t" end="2361890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">他上回也有跟着殿下一同前来</p>
<p begin="2361890000t" end="2385690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">真的是个可怕的家伙</p>
<p begin="2385690000t" end="2415690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我记得那个人的名字是叫樱川九郎</p>
<p begin="2415690000t" end="2456990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">因为吃过人鱼肉才变成不死之身的对吧</p>
<p begin="2456990000t" end="2486990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">不死之身啊 那真是不容小觑</p>
<p begin="2486990000t" end="2516200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">但这点程度的能力也不少怪物有啊</p>
<p begin="2516200000t" end="2560790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">然而他还吃了另一种妖怪</p>
<p begin="2560790000t" end="2595890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">就因为这样 获得了更令人害怕的力量</p>
<p begin="2595890000t" end="2623790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">幸好他现在很听公主殿下的话</p>
<p begin="2623790000t" end="2637200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">要是那个真闹起来</p>
<p begin="2637200000t" end="2670090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我等有几千几万都毫无胜算</p>
<p begin="2682200000t" end="2711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">听起来这公主殿下比传言更有能耐呢</p>
<p begin="2711000000t" end="2723890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">你怎么啦?</p>
<p begin="2723890000t" end="2759800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">难不成是有事想找公主殿下商量吗</p>
<p begin="2759800000t" end="2768990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">是啊</p>
<p begin="2768990000t" end="2788600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我所在的这栋公寓</p>
<p begin="2788600000t" end="2822400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">似乎混入了相当棘手的怪物</p>
<p begin="2828990000t" end="2841100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">一个没搞好</p>
<p begin="2841100000t" end="2872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">说不定咱们也要被绞杀</p>
<p begin="2935400000t" end="2953700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">所以说九郎学长</p>
<p begin="2953700000t" end="2968290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">要不要搬家呢?</p>
<p begin="2972900000t" end="2997090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">为什么会变成这结论</p>
<p begin="2997090000t" end="3037590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我不是说过有个待在公寓的幽灵来咨询吗</p>
<p begin="3047200000t" end="3058390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">正好学长</p>
<p begin="3058390000t" end="3078390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你前阵子不是说在这里有点待不下去</p>
<p begin="3078390000t" end="3108890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">想要搬家吗</p>
<p begin="3108890000t" end="3122200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">是没错</p>
<p begin="3122200000t" end="3140190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">但那是因为邻居都在谣传</p>
<p begin="3140190000t" end="3195190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我带萝莉回家做不可告人的事</p>
<p begin="3206100000t" end="3229390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">你到底做了什么才会传出这种流言</p>
<p begin="3229390000t" end="3241890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">就是你害的啦</p>
<p begin="3246890000t" end="3268190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">谁叫你有事没事跑来我家吵吵闹闹</p>
<p begin="3268190000t" end="3287400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">才会变成这样</p>
<p begin="3287400000t" end="3299100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">那你去好好解释</p>
<p begin="3299100000t" end="3334100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我是跟你念同间大学的女朋友不就好了</p>
<p begin="3334100000t" end="3355400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">我不想撒这种谎</p>
<p begin="3355400000t" end="3376200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">又不用说谎 明明就是事实</p>
<p begin="3376200000t" end="3397900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">我们也确实有做不可告人的事啊</p>
<p begin="3397900000t" end="3428390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">不如说我倒希望你更积极点呢</p>
<p begin="3433390000t" end="3468390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">就是因为你老讲这种话才会有那些谣言</p>
<p begin="3488390000t" end="3497200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">所以</p>
<p begin="3497200000t" end="3524300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">具体来说咨询了什么呢</p>
<p begin="3524300000t" end="3558890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">来咨询的幽灵是那栋公寓的地缚灵</p>
<p begin="3558890000t" end="3594800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">据说它平时主要待在5楼的3号房</p>
<p begin="3594800000t" end="3617300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">因为那一户的住户是个爱看电影的人</p>
<p begin="3617300000t" end="3638990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">它喜欢过去一起看</p>
<p begin="3651490000t" end="3676100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">幽灵也需要一点娱乐吧</p>
<p begin="3676100000t" end="3703700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">然后它说只要在那里待到夜半时分</p>
<p begin="3785790000t" end="3799590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">正上方的房间</p>
<p begin="3799590000t" end="3827500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">就会像是用圆木缓缓敲打地板一样</p>
<p begin="3827500000t" end="3869200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">发出咚咚咚的声音</p>
<p begin="3903000000t" end="3938890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">那个声音虽然没吵到扰人的地步</p>
<p begin="3938890000t" end="3965600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">但有种奇妙的重量感和沉静感</p>
<p begin="3965600000t" end="4018500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">也不像是楼上住户为了骚扰或抱怨发出的</p>
<p begin="4038190000t" end="4074900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">因为声音并不会持续很久</p>
<p begin="4074900000t" end="4103190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">那个住户一开始也没怎么放在心上</p>
<p begin="4110290000t" end="4154100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">但我很早就开始对那个声音打寒颤</p>
<p begin="4154100000t" end="4173700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">一直有种不好的预感</p>
<p begin="4185000000t" end="4218700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">后来住户也觉得这噪音实在太常出现</p>
<p begin="4218700000t" end="4234590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">禁不住烦躁</p>
<p begin="4234590000t" end="4262090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">便去拜托管理员规劝楼上住户</p>
<p begin="4262090000t" end="4280090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">想不到管理员</p>
<p begin="4280090000t" end="4307590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">竟然说正上方的房间已经两个月以上</p>
<p begin="4307590000t" end="4330500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">都没有人住了</p>
<p begin="4340090000t" end="4352200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">好可怕</p>
<p begin="4352200000t" end="4367200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">别急着附和</p>
<p begin="4367200000t" end="4422300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">说不定只是建材热胀冷缩发出的声音啊</p>
<p begin="4422300000t" end="4446490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">这种事挺常见的吧</p>
<p begin="4446490000t" end="4470190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">那样的话只会有轻微的摩擦声吧</p>
<p begin="4470190000t" end="4491890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">不会持续发出缓缓的重击音啊</p>
<p begin="4491890000t" end="4510690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不只如此</p>
<p begin="4510690000t" end="4525690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">管理员也很在意这件事</p>
<p begin="4525690000t" end="4551990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">后来好像就进了楼上的房间</p>
<p begin="4551990000t" end="4590790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">在那间连家具跟窗帘都没有的空房里</p>
<p begin="4609590000t" end="4645400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">有一尊上次进来时没见过的古老人偶</p>
<p begin="4645400000t" end="4668390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">就这样掉在地上</p>
<p begin="4668390000t" end="4697590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">据说那人偶外形实在太过古怪</p>
<p begin="4697590000t" end="4718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">散发着奇异的气息</p>
<p begin="4718000000t" end="4744700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">让他怕得不敢接近</p>
<p begin="4744700000t" end="4761800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">真是太诡异了</p>
<p begin="4761800000t" end="4776390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">人偶真的很可怕</p>
<p begin="4776390000t" end="4807690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">特别是古物更容易带有意念或诅咒</p>
<p begin="4807690000t" end="4835600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">据说管理员最后还是不敢碰那尊人偶</p>
<p begin="4835600000t" end="4857300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">把门锁上就逃了出来</p>
<p begin="4857300000t" end="4891100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">那尊人偶肯定不普通</p>
<p begin="4891100000t" end="4913990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">如果在房里的是正常的幽灵或怪物</p>
<p begin="4913990000t" end="4925690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">应该会现身</p>
<p begin="4925690000t" end="4951990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">也会来找我们打招呼</p>
<p begin="4956200000t" end="4977790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">但这奇物却像是威胁似地</p>
<p begin="4977790000t" end="5001200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">只出声却不现身</p>
<p begin="5007900000t" end="5032090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">也不晓得它究竟在盘算什么</p>
<p begin="5032090000t" end="5065790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">简直像是要一步步地诅咒整栋建筑</p>
<p begin="5071700000t" end="5105500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">如果是那种单方面执行命令的诅咒物品</p>
<p begin="5105500000t" end="5120490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">是没办法沟通的</p>
<p begin="5120490000t" end="5142200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">作为对手相当棘手</p>
<p begin="5142200000t" end="5164700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">管理员已经跟屋主商量</p>
<p begin="5164700000t" end="5198890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">建议找人调查或驱魔</p>
<p begin="5198890000t" end="5219290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">目前晚上仍会听见声音</p>
<p begin="5219290000t" end="5249400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我那房间的住户也无法轻易搬家</p>
<p begin="5249400000t" end="5264400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">十分不安地生活着</p>
<p begin="5270190000t" end="5300700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">我身为地缚灵本来就无法离开这片土地</p>
<p begin="5300700000t" end="5326900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">但我怕得根本不敢上楼</p>
<p begin="5341100000t" end="5358200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">公主殿下 拜托您了</p>
<p begin="5358200000t" end="5391200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">请调查清楚楼上到底有什么</p>
<p begin="5391200000t" end="5415800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">帮助我们恢复平静的生活吧</p>
<p begin="5438300000t" end="5460390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">问题在人偶身上啊…</p>
<p begin="5460390000t" end="5489190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">那么也得调查前住户才行呢</p>
<p begin="5511290000t" end="5525900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">就是这样</p>
<p begin="5525900000t" end="5552200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">在调查那栋公寓的详情之余</p>
<p begin="5552200000t" end="5575090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">干脆顺便搬过去吧</p>
<p begin="5575090000t" end="5597990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">那里离大学也不远</p>
<p begin="5597990000t" end="5617200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">应该正适合你啊</p>
<p begin="5617200000t" end="5654800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">幽灵跟怪物会害怕怪声也太奇怪了吧</p>
<p begin="5659800000t" end="5699400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">那种灵异现象不都是 它们引发来让人类害怕的吗</p>
<p begin="5699400000t" end="5714800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">就算同为怪物</p>
<p begin="5714800000t" end="5725700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">无法对话</p>
<p begin="5725700000t" end="5758200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">不知道会做什么的对象还是很可怕的</p>
<p begin="5758200000t" end="5774090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">就像人类</p>
<p begin="5774090000t" end="5791200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">也有噪音造成的邻居纷争</p>
<p begin="5791200000t" end="5812790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">最后发展成杀人事件的啊</p>
<p begin="5812790000t" end="5834900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">还邻居纷争咧…</p>
<p begin="5834900000t" end="5855000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">不 是没错啦</p>
<p begin="5859090000t" end="5879190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">那我们出发去调查吧</p>
<p begin="5887500000t" end="5902890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">(两天后)</p>
<p begin="5902890000t" end="5918790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">根据我的调查结果</p>
<p begin="5918790000t" end="5954600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">已经确认这栋公寓的声音跟怪异没有关系</p>
<p begin="5966690000t" end="6002990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">只是管理员饲养的宠物跑了出来</p>
<p begin="6002990000t" end="6034700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">躲进那间房间一阵子而已</p>
<p begin="6034700000t" end="6059290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">这公寓有偷工减料的问题</p>
<p begin="6059290000t" end="6083090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">所以有些能钻过的空隙</p>
<p begin="6083090000t" end="6121100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">那只宠物造成的声响传到楼下房间</p>
<p begin="6121100000t" end="6137690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">就成了诡异的声音</p>
<p begin="6137690000t" end="6153200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">那么公主殿下</p>
<p begin="6153200000t" end="6176100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">房间里的古怪人偶又是从哪来的</p>
<p begin="6176100000t" end="6197400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">那是管理员捏造的</p>
<p begin="6197400000t" end="6215700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">实际上根本不存在</p>
<p begin="6215700000t" end="6247000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">说看到人偶跟考虑要驱魔</p>
<p begin="6247000000t" end="6263300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">都是管理员的单方面说法</p>
<p begin="6263300000t" end="6280000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">根本没有其他证人</p>
<p begin="6280000000t" end="6297100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">随他怎么说都行</p>
<p begin="6303700000t" end="6330390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">管理员收到怪声的投诉</p>
<p begin="6330390000t" end="6355900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">注意到他逃跑的宠物在那间房里</p>
<p begin="6355900000t" end="6379700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">就慌忙地跑去把宠物抓回家</p>
<p begin="6379700000t" end="6397990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">如此一来声音就消失了</p>
<p begin="6397990000t" end="6436390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">却抹不去空房里曾有东西发出声音的事实</p>
<p begin="6447590000t" end="6483890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">所以他才想让大家认为声音是怪异造成的</p>
<p begin="6483890000t" end="6513500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">借此隐瞒宠物的存在和逃跑的事</p>
<p begin="6513500000t" end="6536100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">顺带一提这栋公寓是禁止养宠物的</p>
<p begin="6541900000t" end="6578200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">要是被发现身为管理员还违规可是大问题</p>
<p begin="6578200000t" end="6598600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">更遑论还让宠物跑出来</p>
<p begin="6598600000t" end="6622000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">所以他无论如何都必须隐瞒到底</p>
<p begin="6627790000t" end="6650800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">如果他一开始不说是空房</p>
<p begin="6650800000t" end="6683300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">撒谎说有住户造成那个声音</p>
<p begin="6683300000t" end="6712890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">不是就能更简单地蒙混过去吗</p>
<p begin="6712890000t" end="6744600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">只要稍微查一下就知道那里是空房</p>
<p begin="6744600000t" end="6759190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">要是撒了拙劣的谎言</p>
<p begin="6759190000t" end="6785490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">被拆穿时会被质问为什么要说谎</p>
<p begin="6785490000t" end="6800900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">只会更糟糕</p>
<p begin="6800900000t" end="6847200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">所以管理员只能老实承认那间是空房</p>
<p begin="6847200000t" end="6873090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">可是推给怪异的话</p>
<p begin="6873090000t" end="6909800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">不怕住户会吓得离开公寓吗</p>
<p begin="6909800000t" end="6933990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">只要声称人偶已经顺利被驱魔</p>
<p begin="6933990000t" end="6951900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">之后也不再出现声音</p>
<p begin="6951900000t" end="6968200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">问题就解决了</p>
<p begin="6968200000t" end="6999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">因为有问题的是人偶不是房间</p>
<p begin="6999900000t" end="7032000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">也不会损及整栋公寓的风评</p>
<p begin="7032000000t" end="7062000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">但我前天也有听见那个声音</p>
<p begin="7062000000t" end="7078700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">如果他已经抓回宠物的话</p>
<p begin="7078700000t" end="7098700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">应该不会再听见了才对啊</p>
<p begin="7105800000t" end="7137500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">如果管理员去完房间声音就消失</p>
<p begin="7137500000t" end="7162500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">就会表示他有做了什么</p>
<p begin="7167100000t" end="7193400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">"问题是怪异造成"的印象也会变薄弱</p>
<p begin="7193400000t" end="7227990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">也容易令人联想他在那边抓到了什么东西</p>
<p begin="7233790000t" end="7263500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">那么一方面也是为了让人觉得是怪异的错</p>
<p begin="7263500000t" end="7287200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">最好让声音继续出现一阵子</p>
<p begin="7287200000t" end="7312690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">所以他在抓回宠物后</p>
<p begin="7312690000t" end="7335190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">依旧会在半夜偷偷潜进那间空房</p>
<p begin="7335190000t" end="7373990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">踩踏地板让楼下听见类似的声音</p>
<p begin="7373990000t" end="7401900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">有必要为了隐瞒宠物做到这种地步吗</p>
<p begin="7401900000t" end="7426490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">管理员违规在先或许有失颜面</p>
<p begin="7426490000t" end="7460290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">但为了这样做更多坏事不会太大费周章吗</p>
<p begin="7460290000t" end="7482400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">我说的宠物可不是一般的猫狗</p>
<p begin="7494500000t" end="7510800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">是大型的爬虫类</p>
<p begin="7517500000t" end="7539090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">而且是民众在国内饲养的话</p>
<p begin="7539090000t" end="7557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">可能会违法的品种</p>
<p begin="7563790000t" end="7593790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">加上还有公寓偷工减料的问题</p>
<p begin="7593790000t" end="7615090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">比起发生灵异现象</p>
<p begin="7615090000t" end="7640490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">让人知道公寓建筑上的问题</p>
<p begin="7640490000t" end="7670490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">更有可能被住户究责</p>
<p begin="7670490000t" end="7696000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">也会直接影响到经营</p>
<p begin="7696000000t" end="7708890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">作为管理员</p>
<p begin="7708890000t" end="7735590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">这件事无论如何都必须隐瞒到底</p>
<p begin="7741390000t" end="7763500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">爬 爬虫类吗…</p>
<p begin="7763500000t" end="7786100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">从别的意义来说令我害怕啊</p>
<p begin="7786100000t" end="7806490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我还活着的时候就不太能接受…</p>
<p begin="7806490000t" end="7820700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">真是太惊人了</p>
<p begin="7820700000t" end="7853600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">这就是所谓的风声鹤唳吗</p>
<p begin="7853600000t" end="7869500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">咱们完全被骗倒了呢</p>
<p begin="7869500000t" end="7896200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">这管理员真是惹人厌啊</p>
<p begin="7896200000t" end="7925000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">没想到我竟然为了这等小事就怕得不得了</p>
<p begin="7925000000t" end="7945390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">作为幽灵的道行真是差得远了呢</p>
<p begin="7950390000t" end="7988300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">我已经逼问管理员让他说出事情经过</p>
<p begin="7988300000t" end="8007100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">也不会再发出声音了</p>
<p begin="8007100000t" end="8043790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我不打算让这件事张扬到人类社会</p>
<p begin="8043790000t" end="8074700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">要是张扬出去 这里会变得很吵杂</p>
<p begin="8074700000t" end="8096390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">你们也不好过日子吧</p>
<p begin="8096390000t" end="8127200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">所以作为当作没这回事的代价</p>
<p begin="8127200000t" end="8166390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">我要求管理人让九郎学长便宜租下那房间</p>
<p begin="8166390000t" end="8213600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">您有好好惩罚那狡猾的管理员了呢</p>
<p begin="8213600000t" end="8229800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">真是高招 公主殿下</p>
<p begin="8229800000t" end="8245290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">果然严苛</p>
<p begin="8245290000t" end="8268600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">不 根本只是恐吓</p>
<p begin="8268600000t" end="8295290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">不可以用人类的标准来判断</p>
<p begin="8302000000t" end="8332000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">那么 这件事就此解决</p>
<p begin="8396290000t" end="8440490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">(其神之名)</p>
<p begin="8444600000t" end="8470900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">谢谢公主殿下</p>
<p begin="8512990000t" end="8548890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">有必要对幽灵它们隐瞒真相吗</p>
<p begin="8548890000t" end="8570590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">刚才的说明几乎都是假的吧</p>
<p begin="8570590000t" end="8594800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">明明真的有诡异的人偶</p>
<p begin="8594800000t" end="8623090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">也确实是造成楼上噪音的原因</p>
<p begin="8623090000t" end="8666490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">它们本来就深信走错一步可能会被绞杀</p>
<p begin="8666490000t" end="8699500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">没必要再让它们更害怕吧</p>
<p begin="8704900000t" end="8722000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">反正管理员跟屋主</p>
<p begin="8722000000t" end="8762500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">也很感谢我们愿意接手处理人偶</p>
<p begin="8762500000t" end="8782100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">虽然想处理但自己不敢碰</p>
<p begin="8782100000t" end="8811690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">请人驱魔不是被拒绝就是临阵脱逃</p>
<p begin="8811690000t" end="8855490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">他们也说了放着不管会影响公寓风评</p>
<p begin="8855490000t" end="8885090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">就算不收入住的押金跟礼金</p>
<p begin="8885090000t" end="8911790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">再把租金打对折也很值得了</p>
<p begin="8925090000t" end="8966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">再来只要靠我们处理掉人偶就行了</p>
<p begin="8989290000t" end="9011900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">那个人偶到底是什么东西</p>
<p begin="9011900000t" end="9040590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">感觉跟那个匹诺曹又不太一样</p>
<p begin="9040590000t" end="9056900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">那个是诅咒人偶</p>
<p begin="9056900000t" end="9086900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">这个则是好几百年前制作的咒物</p>
<p begin="9086900000t" end="9107790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">是用于驱除放置地点附近的</p>
<p begin="9107790000t" end="9142790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">恶魔和怪物的土偶</p>
<p begin="9142790000t" end="9163700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">算是强力的辟邪道具吧</p>
<p begin="9171200000t" end="9203300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">以前应该是被放在 历史悠久的建筑或土地上</p>
<p begin="9203300000t" end="9224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">发挥其应有的功能吧</p>
<p begin="9224600000t" end="9249600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">随着时间流逝 失去守护的地方</p>
<p begin="9249600000t" end="9288790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">人偶也停止了功能 被随意丢弃了吧</p>
<p begin="9296690000t" end="9325490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">后来可能被那间房的前住户捡到</p>
<p begin="9325490000t" end="9344700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">就把它带了回去</p>
<p begin="9344700000t" end="9356790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">结果住户搬家时</p>
<p begin="9356790000t" end="9392200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">又把它丢在不起眼的地方没带走</p>
<p begin="9392200000t" end="9427690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">房里还有人住时没发生什么怪事吗</p>
<p begin="9427690000t" end="9439800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">即便是咒物</p>
<p begin="9439800000t" end="9466900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">只要停止功能就只是个人偶而已</p>
<p begin="9466900000t" end="9520290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">大概是在搬离时偶然 做了什么近似施咒的事才启动的</p>
<p begin="9526100000t" end="9540700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">这种类型的多半是</p>
<p begin="9540700000t" end="9577000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">在特定部位沾上血或口水来启动</p>
<p begin="9577000000t" end="9608700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">的确是可能会不小心沾到的东西呢</p>
<p begin="9608700000t" end="9621200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">在那之后</p>
<p begin="9621200000t" end="9662100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">人偶内含的意念便会在夜晚化为形体</p>
<p begin="9662100000t" end="9700900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">保护那间空房不受妖怪们的威胁</p>
<p begin="9700900000t" end="9720090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">为什么只在晚上出现?</p>
<p begin="9720090000t" end="9754700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">幽灵跟怪物主要是在夜晚活动</p>
<p begin="9754700000t" end="9783890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">所以人偶才会只在这段时间启动吧</p>
<p begin="9783890000t" end="9813500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">而人偶会保护其所在的地方</p>
<p begin="9813500000t" end="9832690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">也不会离开那间房间</p>
<p begin="9838090000t" end="9860190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">如果待在那栋公寓的幽灵</p>
<p begin="9860190000t" end="9882690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">跑去那间房间探勘情况的话</p>
<p begin="9882690000t" end="9905700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">肯定会被驱除吧</p>
<p begin="9912790000t" end="9934900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">而且已经觉醒力量的人偶</p>
<p begin="9934900000t" end="9970290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">可能也只有我这种等级的人才移动得了</p>
<p begin="9976200000t" end="10016590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">幸好有趁白天把它移到林子里</p>
<p begin="10016590000t" end="10052890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">我也先指示了周遭的妖怪们不要靠近那里</p>
<p begin="10122590000t" end="10157990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">那个可能会无差别铲除幽灵和怪物的人偶</p>
<p begin="10157990000t" end="10182990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">对现今的时代实在是太危险了</p>
<p begin="10182990000t" end="10211000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">就我的立场来说 也只能将其破坏</p>
<p begin="10215190000t" end="10242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">但是直接破坏人偶的话</p>
<p begin="10242300000t" end="10269800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">反而会释放它内含的意念</p>
<p begin="10269800000t" end="10293580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">处理起来会更加棘手</p>
<p begin="10293580000t" end="10305190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">所以只能在夜晚</p>
<p begin="10305190000t" end="10336500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">破坏那个自行出现的意念</p>
<p begin="10439500000t" end="10465390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">那就是你所谓的 人偶的真身吗</p>
<p begin="10465390000t" end="10477100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">没错</p>
<p begin="10477100000t" end="10491700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">看来这个除魔的意念</p>
<p begin="10491700000t" end="10532100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">一开始就做成与人偶本身相同的外貌呢</p>
<p begin="10541700000t" end="10555890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">话说回来这个人偶</p>
<p begin="10555890000t" end="10577990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">为什么会做成力士的样子?</p>
<p begin="10589300000t" end="10618090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">力士本来就是形容力量强大的人物</p>
<p begin="10618090000t" end="10643090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">考古时甚至找到许多形似力士的土俑</p>
<p begin="10643090000t" end="10658490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">是自古就有的存在</p>
<p begin="10662690000t" end="10682690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">也有神明就叫金刚力士</p>
<p begin="10682690000t" end="10707690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">以驱魔人来说是相当适合的形象</p>
<p begin="10713190000t" end="10738190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">相扑同时是一种祭神活动</p>
<p begin="10738190000t" end="10756900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">也有一种说法是开场时踏的四股</p>
<p begin="10756900000t" end="10790690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">就是为了镇压地底恶灵的仪式</p>
<p begin="10803190000t" end="10826600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">然后从那房间传出的重音</p>
<p begin="10826600000t" end="10858690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">就是这个意念踏出四股的声音</p>
<p begin="10865000000t" end="10886190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">这是为镇压恶灵做的行为</p>
<p begin="10886190000t" end="10921300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">也难怪楼下的幽灵会害怕</p>
<p begin="10927990000t" end="10939200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">因为踏的不是地面</p>
<p begin="10939200000t" end="10957100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">传出去的力道变弱</p>
<p begin="10957100000t" end="10982200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">才不至于把那个幽灵直接驱除掉</p>
<p begin="10998900000t" end="11021400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">诡异声音的真面目居然是四股</p>
<p begin="11021400000t" end="11034300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">也太惊人了</p>
<p begin="11034300000t" end="11050590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">真是令人意外的真相呢</p>
<p begin="11050590000t" end="11073090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">不不不 这感觉会挨骂吧</p>
<p begin="11073090000t" end="11100190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">顺带一提那房间的前住户</p>
<p begin="11100190000t" end="11124400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">是学生相扑的佼佼者</p>
<p begin="11124400000t" end="11160690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">大概也是因此才会 在看见力士造型的旧人偶时</p>
<p begin="11160690000t" end="11184900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">忍不住带回家当作幸运物吧</p>
<p begin="11198590000t" end="11226600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">可能是多亏如此 他的赛绩不错</p>
<p begin="11226600000t" end="11254100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">但是不久前受了重伤引退</p>
<p begin="11254100000t" end="11290390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">也因此不愿继续带着人偶</p>
<p begin="11290390000t" end="11312890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">但是也不敢直接丢掉</p>
<p begin="11312890000t" end="11340890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">才选择留在房里的</p>
<p begin="11357990000t" end="11374200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">就是这样 九郎学长</p>
<p begin="11379700000t" end="11408800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">请照我们说好的跟那个战斗吧</p>
<p begin="11408800000t" end="11422990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">这样事件就解决咯</p>
<p begin="11434300000t" end="11453900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">它看起来很强欸</p>
<p begin="11453900000t" end="11486800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">而且这个力士有四只手臂 头上还长角</p>
<p begin="11486800000t" end="11500590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">到底是想怎样</p>
<p begin="11500590000t" end="11524000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">是制作人偶的人的兴趣吧</p>
<p begin="11524000000t" end="11545690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">觉得只做成力士的样子还不太够</p>
<p begin="11545690000t" end="11578590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">就加上感觉很强的独角仙的形象之类的</p>
<p begin="11584900000t" end="11598590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">独角仙…</p>
<p begin="11604000000t" end="11617400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">我可以逃跑吗</p>
<p begin="11617400000t" end="11654900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">它可是会自动驱除怪物和怪异的哦</p>
<p begin="11654900000t" end="11697890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">一旦注意到比怪异更妖异 被怪异们畏惧的你接近</p>
<p begin="11697890000t" end="11711700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">肯定会立刻袭击过来</p>
<p begin="11722100000t" end="11738800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">它注意到我们了呢</p>
<p begin="11772500000t" end="11790090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">还有因为我是神的关系</p>
<p begin="11790090000t" end="11806700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">不会被它攻击</p>
<p begin="11806700000t" end="11827990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">不用在意我 放心战斗吧</p>
<p begin="12011500000t" end="12029500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">话说回来那位九郎大人</p>
<p begin="12029500000t" end="12067000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">好像因为吃了另一种妖怪获得可怕的力量</p>
<p begin="12067000000t" end="12082400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">是什么力量啊</p>
<p begin="12091600000t" end="12125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">那位九郎大人吃了"件"</p>
<p begin="12125000000t" end="12137890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">你说"件"</p>
<p begin="12137890000t" end="12165890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">是那个会预言未来并死亡的怪物吗</p>
<p begin="12165890000t" end="12181700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">难道九郎大人获得了那个能力</p>
<p begin="12181700000t" end="12200890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">可以看见未来?</p>
<p begin="12200890000t" end="12221700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">不只能看见未来</p>
<p begin="12221700000t" end="12250890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">据说还能决定自己想要的未来呢</p>
<p begin="12250890000t" end="12274300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">虽然似乎不是任何未来都能决定</p>
<p begin="12274300000t" end="12296800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">不过只要有一定程度的可能性</p>
<p begin="12296800000t" end="12325990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">就必定能实现他的选择</p>
<p begin="12330590000t" end="12353490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">也就是说他能操纵未来吗</p>
<p begin="12353490000t" end="12372300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">真是可怕</p>
<p begin="12372300000t" end="12400290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">可是件平常不是预言完就会死掉吗</p>
<p begin="12400290000t" end="12408190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">不</p>
<p begin="12408190000t" end="12434900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">应该说是因为接受死亡才能预言未来</p>
<p begin="12434900000t" end="12459100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">那么九郎大人要使用那份力量</p>
<p begin="12459100000t" end="12473190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">也不可能平安无事才对</p>
<p begin="12473190000t" end="12492000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">也不用那么怕他吧</p>
<p begin="12492000000t" end="12532890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">不 九郎大人是吃了人鱼肉的不死之身</p>
<p begin="12532890000t" end="12557890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">就算用了件的力量也能复活</p>
<p begin="12562500000t" end="12606700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">他似乎就是透过死亡来使用件的能力</p>
<p begin="12606700000t" end="12638390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">也就是以自己的生命为代价来操纵未来</p>
<p begin="12851090000t" end="12887400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">这么说的话 就算杀死九郎大人…</p>
<p begin="12902790000t" end="12939500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">他也会抓住反击的未来并复活</p>
<p begin="12939500000t" end="12956190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">无论杀几次都没有用</p>
<p begin="12956190000t" end="12983290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">有谁赢得了这种怪物呢</p>
<p begin="13111400000t" end="13125590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">可谓是…</p>
<p begin="13125590000t" end="13145590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">货真价实的怪物!</p>
<p begin="13397890000t" end="13413390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">学长 太完美了</p>
<p begin="13885090000t" end="13916400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">难道没有更轻松的赢法吗</p>
<p begin="13921400000t" end="13944700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">虽然成功死了一次决定这个未来</p>
<p begin="13944700000t" end="13966400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">但我也受了挺重的伤耶</p>
<p begin="13966400000t" end="13994800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">你的身体马上就会复原</p>
<p begin="13994800000t" end="14015990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">而且也没有痛觉不是吗</p>
<p begin="14021900000t" end="14051500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">我也是心不甘情不愿地</p>
<p begin="14051500000t" end="14081090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">用了喜欢的手杖去刺妖怪耶</p>
<p begin="14089000000t" end="14121090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">应该有不需要让你亲自涉险的方法吧</p>
<p begin="14121090000t" end="14144900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">这点程度不算危险啊</p>
<p begin="14150290000t" end="14175790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">多亏九郎学长挺身而出</p>
<p begin="14191600000t" end="14206190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">这次的事挺微不足道的</p>
<p begin="14215000000t" end="14250390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">我得在发生争执时协调妖怪间的利害关系</p>
<p begin="14250390000t" end="14272990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">如果还扯进人类</p>
<p begin="14272990000t" end="14286700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">就得多方注意和安排</p>
<p begin="14286700000t" end="14315490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">把大事化小 小事化无</p>
<p begin="14315490000t" end="14335090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">相较那些麻烦事</p>
<p begin="14335090000t" end="14350490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">这次真的很轻松了</p>
<p begin="14363900000t" end="14380590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">只要打倒就能解决的事</p>
<p begin="14380590000t" end="14403490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">确实是挺简单明了的</p>
<p begin="14403490000t" end="14420990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">那么我们就回家吧</p>
<p begin="14420990000t" end="14456090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">早上还得去大学呢</p>
<p begin="14461500000t" end="14486500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">你该不会又堆着报告没写吧</p>
<p begin="14493190000t" end="14534100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">忙着处理妖怪的委托可不能当借口哦</p>
<p begin="14534100000t" end="14562790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">那就请你作为男友帮帮我吧</p>
<p begin="14562790000t" end="14588290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">报告不自己做就没意义了吧</p>
<p begin="14795090000t" end="14816800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">我的名字是岩永琴子</p>
<p begin="14833490000t" end="14881900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">是守护妖怪 幽灵 怪异 魔物…</p>
<p begin="14881900000t" end="14901900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">被这么称呼的物种们</p>
<p begin="14901900000t" end="14920290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">并维持这个世界秩序的</p>
<p begin="14933190000t" end="14947000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">智慧之神</p>
<p begin="14970290000t" end="15000390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">(待续)</p>
